ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.280                Enzyme
NAME        N,N'-diacetylchitobiose phosphorylase;
            chbP (gene name)
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     N,N'-diacetylchitobiose:phosphate N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyltransferase
REACTION    N,N'-diacetylchitobiose + phosphate = N-acetyl-D-glucosamine + N-acetyl-alpha-D-glucosamine 1-phosphate [RN:R09942]
ALL_REAC    R09942
SUBSTRATE   N,N'-diacetylchitobiose [CPD:C01674];
            phosphate [CPD:C00009]
PRODUCT     N-acetyl-D-glucosamine [CPD:C00140];
            N-acetyl-alpha-D-glucosamine 1-phosphate [CPD:C04501]
COMMENT     The enzyme is specific for N,N'-diacetylchitobiose and does not phosphorylate other N-acetylchitooligosaccharides, cellobiose, trehalose, lactose, maltose or sucrose.
